data.description: Welcome to Woodgate! This 1620sf, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhouse has it all with one of the best floor plans in Woodgate. As an end unit there is an abundance of natural light.  Oversized windows in your spacious Living room/Dining room area, look out to the open side lot with mature trees and beautifully maintained lawn. Kitchen has been updated with granite counter top and backsplash. The door wall opens to the well attended enclosed private garden and patio with brick pavers. Spend winter evenings in the adjoining family room with your cozy gas fireplace. Master  Primary bedroom has a large walk in closet and master bath with walk in shower. Two additional bedrooms share the other full bath. New roof 2018 and vinyl siding 2021. New AC and Water Heater 2022. Pool and clubhouse are added amenities. DTP is a short walk, less than a mile, for you to enjoy all this city has to offer; the shops, restaurants, festivals and easy access to freeways. HOA includes gas, water, trash pickup, snow removal, and grounds maintenance.  Come see why Woodgate is the best kept secret in Plymouth. This opportunity won't last long!
